metadata.name: Betwixt Braves #1
metadata.description:
Betwixt is an interactive story that takes you on an epic journey of self-exploration. Discover a magical world on the border of your reality and imagination, develop mental resilience, and befriend the voice in your head.

This NFT unlocks the first chapter of Betwixt for free and gives you exclusive access to our Elder NFT collection — mint to play the full 11-chapter journey and generate your own, unique art based on the choices you make in the game.

To receive the full utility, you need to “ascend” by burning your mask here: https://braves.betwixt.life/#/.

Watch your NFT transform into a surprise glimpse of the world of Betwixt and start playing for free.
